WEBVTT

30:01.650 --> 30:02.317
Sudhakar!

30:05.317 --> 30:06.150
Where are you?

30:06.859 --> 30:07.942
There you are!

30:08.109 --> 30:09.942
Thought I'll leave you if you hide?

30:09.942 --> 30:11.484
Dad, no please.

30:11.609 --> 30:13.442
Please don't dad, it's paining.

30:13.484 --> 30:15.067
You want treatment?
Here is your treatment.

30:15.067 --> 30:17.609
-I am your doctor, say thank you.
-It hurts.

30:17.692 --> 30:18.775
Will you ever paint again?

30:18.817 --> 30:19.942
Not because I like it.

30:20.400 --> 30:23.650
I became a painter just
because my dad hated it.

30:28.109 --> 30:28.900
What is this thing?

30:29.400 --> 30:31.400
How do you categorize this bullshit?

30:31.400 --> 30:33.942
Awfully bad painting in
the pretence of modern art.

30:34.150 --> 30:35.359
Such a waste of time.
